title: Ranagade on Being Snoop Dogg’s Full Time Bl**t Roller & More
description:
Ranagade came out swinging in this God Tier episode! She talks about recently going viral after being hired as Snoop's roller, shares her amazing story, career tips, empowering messages and more! Welcome back Dizaster! https://www.instagram.com/ranagadeper...

---
00:00 Intro
1:25 Lush comes for Ranagade from the jump! 
1:51 "She wraps her mouth around this" - Ranagade claps back!
3:00 How she got the job with Snoop + Rolling the one in Rogan/Elon Musk pod episode
6:06 Works with Jadakiss + JR Smith, Kid Cudi, etc
8:00 Lush comes for Ranagade again: "Why is he coming for me??"
10:15 Proud Iranian woman, gets back at Lush heavily 
14:25 Developing blunt rolling bars and sessions at events and parties + Getting gigs on MTV as well 
16:42 AD says someone should make a movie about her life and her success story 
17:41 Ranagade kicks a freestyle targeted at Lush + She and Lush got at each other again: "You don't want no smoke"
21:10 Her name was given to her around the release of the Jayz and Em song "Renegade"
22:40 Growing up in Cincinnati when she moved to the states
25:05 Ranagade was flabbergasted on why her parents landed in Cincinnati, but in hindsight, she got the real US experience in the midwest + White kids used to call her n___ growing up 
30:53 Da Brat shouted her out + Her hands are insured 
34:55 Handed perfectly rolled blunts to YSL, Rihanna 
36:44 How Elon Musk endedup smoking her blunt on the Joe Rogan Show
37:25 Using all natural adhesive to roll blunts 
44:56 Rana cannot disclose how much money she makes, but she's living good off her hard work 47:06 Rana brought gifts 
48:56 S/O Snoop's Premium 
50:23 Rana has a rolling kit, watch out for the knocks offs out there
53:59 Rana gives Diz his flowers and the whole battle rap scene, being fan of Dizaster
57:17 Diz interrupts her story on how she got the job for her skills not her looks to tell a random Snoop story 
59:07 Rana delivers a powerful women empowerment message, having a clear conscious, moving right, being a good person not relying on your looks 
1:01:23 Rana gives the ultimate sauce on how she keeps her leaves fresh 
1:06:08 Has a PHD in blunt rolling 
1:09:35 Rana pulls out her adhesive product 
1:13:05 Blunt is ready + Diz just grabs it and starts smoking, without showing the final product
1:14:04 Rana gives props to Lush for his sobriety 
1:16:00 Diz won't say she rolls better than him but..
1:17:39 Rana was about to visit Iran before the whole situation happened + Pays respects to Iranian women + Her hard work is for all women who are not allowed to be free
1:24:07 Diz and Rana are the american dream for people where they come from 
1:24:30 Rana appreciates the fact that she is able to do what she does and live free, hopes to inspire one person at a time
